could you check `vk == winapi::um::winuser::VK_RMEN` first please? it is cheaper than  LOWORD, though a very little bit, :).
``` 
if vk == winapi::um::winuser::VK_RMENU as u16 && winapi::shared::minwindef::LOWORD(LAYOUT as usize 
                  vk = winapi::um::winuser::VK_HANGUL as u16;
            }
```

I modified it a little. 
`            if (LAYOUT as u16 == 0x0412) && (vk == winapi::um::winuser::VK_RMENU as u16) { 
                vk = winapi::um::winuser::VK_HANGUL as u16;
            }
`
